The band released one album before they split up. One thousand copies were printed, and all the copies were promptly sold, save for a few kept by the band members. However due to the band breaking up, no more copies were printed, and the album faded into obscurity. This is a torrent of that album (minus a couple of songs). This album is really good. You might even like it if you\\\'ve never liked a folk song before in your life. It\\\'s one of those rare gems that failed to reach broad exposure, not because of lack of quality, but because of all the other reasons good things fail to get noticed.

All but two tracks are included in this torrent. Those tracks can\\\'t be included because of copyright reasons. That\\\'s too bad, because they are pretty good tracks. I guess if someone else were to upload another torrent with those tracks included, there would be nothing I could do about it...

